The paper discusses the optimization of Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs) for sequence-based problems, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence research (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). The focus is on improving the efficiency and execution time of these networks, which is relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) tasks.
